        achieve is_on(fryingpan) # Ensure the frying pan is heated
        achieve inside(eggs, fryingpan) # Pour the beaten eggs into the heated frying pan

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind fryingpan: item where:
            is_fryingpan(fryingpan)
        # Select the frying pan for heating the eggs
        
        bind eggs: item where:
            is_bowl(eggs) and close_char(char, eggs)
        # Select the bowl with beaten eggs which should be close to the character
        
        heat_frying_pan_and_pour_eggs(fryingpan, eggs)

behavior heat_frying_pan_and_pour_eggs(fryingpan:item, bowl:item):
    body:
        achieve plugged(fryingpan) # Ensure the frying pan is plugged in
        achieve is_on(fryingpan) # Turn on the frying pan to heat it
        achieve close(bowl, fryingpan) # Ensure the bowl with eggs is close to the frying pan
        achieve inside(bowl, fryingpan) # Pour the beaten eggs into the frying pan

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind fryingpan: item where:
            is_fryingpan(fryingpan)
        # Select the frying pan
        
        bind bowl: item where:
            is_bowl(bowl) and dirty(bowl)
        # Select the bowl with beaten eggs
        
        heat_frying_pan_and_pour_eggs(fryingpan, bowl)
